{{!
    @template mod_scorecard/template_import_affordance

    "Import template" affordance shown above the manage tabs for an empty
    scorecard. Caller suppresses this once the scorecard has any items or
    bands per Phase 6.5b Q-rework-2.

    Context variables required:
    * importurl  - Absolute URL to template_import.php?cmid=<cmid>.
    * label      - Lang string template:import:empty:button.
    * tooltip    - Lang string template:import:empty:tooltip.

    Example context (json):
    {
        "importurl": "/mod/scorecard/template_import.php?cmid=42",
        "label": "Import template",
        "tooltip": "Import a JSON template to populate this scorecard."
    }
}}
<div class="scorecard-template-import-affordance mb-3">
    <a href="{{importurl}}" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm" title="{{tooltip}}">{{label}}</a>
</div>
